background: PhD in Computer Science. Expert in Machine Learning and Artificial Intelligence. Worked with Yann LeCun on Convolutional Neural Networks.
PhD in Mathematics. Area of research is topological manifolds. Recipient of the Clay Millennium Prize.

Master of Music. Expert in classical compositions. Worked with Berlin Philharmonic Orchestra.
